column2: SELECT m.objid, m.ra1 AS ra1, m.dec1 AS dec1, n.objid, petroMag_u, petroMagErr_u, petroMag_g, petroMagErr_g, petroMag_r, petroMagErr_r, petroMag_i, petroMagErr_i, petroMag_z, petroMagErr_z, modelMag_u, modelMagErr_u, modelMag_g, modelMagErr_g, modelMag_r, modelMagErr_r, modelMag_i, modelMagErr_i, modelMag_z, modelMagErr_z, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2 into mydb.final_petro from MyDB.final_# AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra1, m.dec1, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObjAll AS o ON n.objid = o.objid
